# Crypto Wallet

A simple project for managing virtual wallets.

## Description

This project provides an interface to view balances and transactions of cryptocurrency wallets. Currently, it uses mock (fake) data for testing purposes.

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/maoroch/crypto-wallet.git
```

2. Go to the project folder:

```bash
cd crypto-wallet
```

3. Create a virtual environment (optional but recommended):

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate   # on macOS/Linux
.venv\Scripts\activate      # on Windows
```

4. Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Running the project

```bash
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

The project will be available at `http://127.0.0.1:8000`.

## Stack

* Python 3.x
* FastAPI
* Uvicorn
* (Optional) Any database you plan to use
